latex: \begin{aligned} \begin{split} \mathbb{E}\left(||\bm{f(x_0)}||^2_2 \right) = & ||\mathbf{ x}^{(0)}||^2_2 \Pi^L_{l=1}\frac{n_l \sigma^{2}_{w,l}}{2} + \sigma^{2}_{b,L} \frac{n_L}{2} + \sum^{L-1}_{l=1} \sigma^{2}_{b,l} \frac{n_l}{2} \Pi^{L}_{k=l+1}\frac{n_k\sigma^{2}_{w,k}}{2}. \end{split} \end{aligned}
